q.ans <- quiz1007[paste("Q", 1:3, sep="")]
q.ans.pdi <- factor(q.ans$Q1, levels=c("", "", "", "", ""), labels=paste(rev(seq(50, 90, by=10)), "%", sep=""))
q.ans.reading <- factor(q.ans$Q2, levels=c("", "", "", ""), labels=c("20", "30", "40", "50 "))
q.ans.hard.times <- factor(q.ans$Q3, levels=c("", "", "", ""), labels=c("", "", "", ""))
q.ans.tbl <- apply(q.ans, 2, table, useNA="ifany")
